data.description: The River Mountain Ranch- Fantastic location & setting overlooking the Salmon River with close access to recreation on the Salmon & Snake Rivers. The home is in immaculate condition, is very well maintained & has numerous updates including an all new, beautifully remodeled kitchen, new flooring throughout, paint, updated baths, & more. This is one of the best quality manufactured homes you'll find. Come enjoy the great natural lighting, the wonderful views of the river throughout the home & the lovely, covered porch overlooking the river & mountains. Outside you have a low maintenance yard with lawn, attractive landscape, mature shade trees, circular gravel drive, & concrete edging all around. Attached garage is finished with work benches & storage. Great water rights & system. No CC&R's.
